<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 15:13:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>刚果释放了大部分因非法采矿而被关押的中国男子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/congo-frees-most-chinese-men-held-illegal-mining-2024-12-25/</link><description>刚果民主共和国当局周二晚间表示，因涉嫌在该国经营非法金矿而被捕的 17 名中国男子中，有 14 人已获释。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 09:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/congo-frees-most-chinese-men-held-illegal-mining-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安夜票房跌至13年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-christmas-eve-box-office-plunges-13-year-low-2024-12-25/</link><description>票务预订平台猫眼周三的数据显示，中国平安夜票房收入暴跌至至少13年来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 09:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-christmas-eve-box-office-plunges-13-year-low-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查再延长三个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-extends-eu-brandy-anti-dumping-investigation-2024-12-25/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，将对原产于欧盟的白兰地的反倾销调查延长三个月，低于此前指导意见允许的全部延长期限。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-extends-eu-brandy-anti-dumping-investigation-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国骗子从鱿鱼游戏中汲取灵感，对负债者进行掠夺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tricksters-take-cue-squid-game-prey-indebted-2024-12-25/</link><description>在中国的“鱿鱼游戏”中，诈骗者通过承诺奖金、债务重组和其他并非总是兑现承诺的计划，以经济衰退中陷入财务困境的人为目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-tricksters-take-cue-squid-game-prey-indebted-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>巴西中场奥斯卡返回圣保罗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</link><description>巴西意甲球队周二表示，前切尔西中场球员奥斯卡将以三年合同回到他的前俱乐部圣保罗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>尽管销量增长，丰田全球产量连续第十个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</link><description>日本汽车制造商丰田汽车周三表示，尽管由于美国和中国需求强劲，其全球销量连续第二个月增长，但该公司 11 月份全球产量连续第 10 个月下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责菲律宾防长就中美导弹问题发表言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</link><description>中国周三谴责菲律宾国防部长有关中国的言论，称其为“毫无根据的指控”，“恶意攻击”中国执政的共产党。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 03:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中日外长同意访日安全对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</link><description>日本周三表示，中日外长在北京举行的会谈为日本明年接待中国外长以及双方同意尽快举行安全对话铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 01:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大谴责中国就维吾尔族和西藏问题针对加拿大机构采取的措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</link><description>加拿大政府周二谴责中国对涉及维吾尔族和西藏人权问题的两家加拿大机构和20名人士采取的措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 21:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国药明康德将在美国限制下出售先进疗法部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</link><description>中国药明康德周二表示，其子公司已与美国私募股权公司 Altaris LLC 签署协议，出售其细胞和基因治疗制造部门 WuXi Advanced Therapies，交易金额未公开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 14:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>本田和日产的合作需要双方都抽不出时间的东西：时间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-nissan-tie-up-requires-something-neither-can-spare-time-2024-12-24/</link><description>本田和日产希望通过合并创建世界第三大汽车集团而获得巨大收益，但来自中国的激烈竞争引发了人们对合并能否及时实现的疑问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 13:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-nissan-tie-up-requires-something-neither-can-spare-time-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着主要国家吝惜援助，全球饥饿危机加深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/global-hunger-crisis-deepens-major-nations-skimp-aid-2024-12-24/</link><description>这是一个简单但残酷的等式：世界各地挨饿或陷入困境的人数正在增加，而世界上最富有的国家为帮助他们而提供的资金却在下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 11:12:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/global-hunger-crisis-deepens-major-nations-skimp-aid-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国和日本预计周三讨论海鲜禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-expected-discuss-seafood-ban-wednesday-2024-12-24/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中国外交部长王毅将于周三在北京与日本外长岩屋毅举行会谈，预计两人将讨论中国对日本海鲜进口的禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 08:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-expected-discuss-seafood-ban-wednesday-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾捍卫美国部署的导弹系统，寻求拥有自己的导弹系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-defends-us-missile-system-deployment-seeks-acquire-its-own-2024-12-24/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周二证明该国部署美国中程导弹系统的合理性，并计划购买自己的中程导弹系统，尽管遭到南海长期竞争对手中国的反对。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 07:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-defends-us-missile-system-deployment-seeks-acquire-its-own-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>曼联杯主席表示，尽管退役，但比赛仍处于良好状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/game-good-hands-despite-high-profile-retirements-says-united-cup-chief-2024-12-24/</link><description>这项价值 1000 万美元的混合团体赛事颇受欢迎，旨在在周五新赛季拉开帷幕时培养新人才。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 07:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/game-good-hands-despite-high-profile-retirements-says-united-cup-chief-2024-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>